title: Australian cricketer David Warner arrives in Sydney after scandal
text:
Australian cricketer David Warner arrives in Sydney after scandal 1:39am EDT - 01:18 
Australian cricketer David Warner arrived in Sydney comforted by wife Candice and their children after a ball-tampering scandal that has rocked the sport. No reporter narration.
